PRIMARY school pupils in Ayrshire have scooped an international award for their work on a Global Citizenship Initiative. International win for pupils PRIMARY school pupils in Ayrshire have scooped an international award for their work on a Global Citizenship Initiative.Caledonia Primary School in Saltcoats has achieved the British Council's International School Award 2014-2017.The school submitted its Impact Evaluation of international learning activities which wowed the judges and secured its new international status. 